  <chunk id="e703a33d5803f827c3d57a19385c0c2cbc2830e9.c5" text="Conclusion: Parvoviral enteritis is predominant among puppies. Yet, bacteria and their toxins also play an important role in HGE. Gentamicin has higher sensitivity against the enteropathogens associated with the condition.">
